{{Vgname|1=平壤賽車|ko=평양 레이서|en=Pyongyang Racer}}是一款于2012年由{{tsl|en|Nosotek}}製作，並由{{tsl|en|Koryo Tours|高麗旅行社}}發行的一款的[[竞速游戏|竞速游戏]]。在該遊戲中，玩家可在[[平壤市|平壤市]]周圍駕駛{{tsl|en|Hwiparam II}}汽車並在收集燃料與避開其餘車輛的同時參觀若干景點。該遊戲作爲一家組織赴朝鮮旅游的[[旅行社|旅行社]]高麗旅行社的[[廣告遊戲|廣告遊戲]]而製作，並由外包公司{{tsl|en|Nosotek}}與[[金策工業綜合大學|金策工業綜合大學]]學生聯合開發。作爲朝鮮爲數不多的電子遊戲之一，《平壤賽車》于2012年12月由高麗旅行社通過其官網發佈。遊戲評論家們批評了該遊戲的玩法、圖像、操控和音樂。

== 遊戲玩法 ==
《平壤賽車》的遊戲地點位於[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鮮]]首都[[平壤市|平壤市]]<ref name="Vice: History">{{Cite web|title=North Korea's First Racing Video Game Is Terrible|url=https://www.vice.com/en/article/avnpwz/north-koreas-first-racing-video-game-is-terrible|access-date=2022-04-23|work=www.vice.com|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142230/https://www.vice.com/en/article/avnpwz/north-koreas-first-racing-video-game-is-terrible|dead-url=no}}</ref>，玩家負責操控一輛{{tsl|en|Hwiparam II}}型汽車（由朝鮮汽車製造商[[平和自動車|平和自動車]]負責製造）<ref name="Koryo Tours: History">{{Cite web|title=Pyongyang Racer North Korean Video Game - Koryo Tours|url=https://koryogroup.com/blog/north-korea-game-pyongyang-racer|access-date=2022-04-23|work=koryogroup.com|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142234/https://koryogroup.com/blog/north-korea-game-pyongyang-racer|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使用[[方向鍵|方向鍵]]加速、倒車和轉向，使用[[空格键|空格键]]鳴響{{tsl|en|Vehicle horn|汽車喇叭}}<ref name="HG101: Review">{{Cite web|title=Pyongyang Racer – Hardcore Gaming 101|url=http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/pyongyang-racer/|access-date=2022-04-23|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142241/http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/pyongyang-racer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩家的任務是沿著遊戲預定路綫在平壤周圍行駛，起點與終點均爲[[金日成廣場|金日成廣場]]。並途中參觀幾個景點，包括[[柳京飯店|柳京飯店]]、[[平壤凱旋門|平壤凱旋門]]、[[千里馬銅像|千里馬銅像]]以及[[普通門|普通門]]<ref name="Koryo Tours: History" /><ref name="The Mary Sue: Review" />，遊戲通過一個視綫，授予玩家該位置的印章，並顯示有關該對象的信息<ref name="HG101: Review" /><ref name="Jalopnik: Review">{{Cite web|title=The First North Korean Racing Game Is A Perfect Metaphor For Their Society|url=https://jalopnik.com/the-first-north-korean-racing-game-is-a-perfect-metapho-5970241|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Jalopnik|language=en-us|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142241/https://jalopnik.com/the-first-north-korean-racing-game-is-a-perfect-metapho-5970241|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在駕駛過程中，玩家必須多次收集{{tsl|en|fuel tank|油箱}}以防止[[油量錶|油量錶]]的自動耗盡<ref name="HG101: Review" /><ref name="Polygon: News">{{Cite web|title=The first game developed in North Korea is a browser racing game for tourists|url=https://www.polygon.com/2012/12/20/3787904/the-first-game-developed-in-north-korea-is-a-browser-racing-game-for|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2012-12-20|last=Corriea|first=Alexa Ray|work=Polygon|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142325/https://www.polygon.com/2012/12/20/3787904/the-first-game-developed-in-north-korea-is-a-browser-racing-game-for|dead-url=no}}</ref>，與靜止的車輛發生三次碰撞則會導致遊戲重置<ref name="The Mary Sue: Review">{{Cite web|title=North Korea Develops Racing Game for Travel Agency|url=https://www.themarysue.com/north-korea-racing-game/|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2012-12-20|work=The Mary Sue|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142243/https://www.themarysue.com/north-korea-racing-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kotaku: News">{{Cite web|title=This Game Was Developed in North Korea. Play It Right Now.|url=https://kotaku.com/this-game-was-developed-in-north-korea-play-it-right-n-5970058|access-date=2022-04-23|work=Kotaku|language=en-us|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142327/https://kotaku.com/this-game-was-developed-in-north-korea-play-it-right-n-5970058|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲中沒有行人<ref name="Kotaku: News" />，若玩家轉向了錯誤的道路則會被[[交通警察|交通警察]]訓責，而當玩家開車離開錯誤車道時會被放回街道上<ref name="HG101: Review" /><ref name="Jalopnik: Review" />。遊戲以[[計時賽|計時賽]]的方式記錄玩家完成遊戲所需的時間<ref name="Koryo Tours: History" />，高麗旅行社會爲玩家的遊戲時間保存一個[[得分|得分]]記錄。并在玩家通過[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]的方式傳送遊戲結果的屏幕[[截圖|截圖]]時更新該記錄<ref name="The Verge: News">{{Cite web|title=Play this: 'Pyongyang Racer' is the first game developed in North Korea for Western audiences|url=https://www.theverge.com/2012/12/20/3788332/play-this-pyongyang-racer-first-north-korea-game|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2012-12-20|last=Welch|first=Chris|work=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142327/https://www.theverge.com/2012/12/20/3788332/play-this-pyongyang-racer-first-north-korea-game|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 開發與發佈 ==
《平壤賽車》是少數由朝鮮開發的遊戲之一<ref name="HG101: History">{{Cite web|title=Hardcore Gaming 101: A History of Korean Gaming|url=http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/korea/specials/special-northkorea.htm|access-date=2022-04-23|work=hardcoregaming101|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142645/http://www.hardcoregaming101.net/korea/specials/special-northkorea.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，据媒體報道，該遊戲為朝鮮第一款面相國際玩家開發的遊戲<ref name="The Verge: News" /><ref name="Kill Screen: News">{{Cite web|title=The first North Korean English-language video game is the best indie game of the year|url=https://killscreen.com/previously/articles/first-north-korean-english-language-video-game-best-indie-game-year/|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2012-12-20|last=Bernstein|first=Joseph|work=Kill Screen - Previously|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142751/https://killscreen.com/previously/articles/first-north-korean-english-language-video-game-best-indie-game-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該遊戲由2007年創立的[[德國|德國]]-[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|朝鮮]]合資[[信息技术|信息技术]]公司{{tsl|en|Nosotek}}製作，總部設於[[平壤市|平壤市]]，主要業務之一即在[[外包|外包]]的基礎之上開發[[手机游戏|手机游戏]]和基於[[Adobe_Flash|Adobe Flash]]系統的遊戲，其中一些遊戲則由德國[[柏林|柏林]]公司Exozet發佈<ref name="HG101: History" /><ref name="Computerworld: Nosotek">{{Cite web|title=The world's most unusual outsourcing destination|url=https://www.computerworld.com/article/2518915/the-world-s-most-unusual-outsourcing-destination.html|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2010-06-10|last=Williams|first=Martyn|work=Computerworld|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142749/https://www.computerworld.com/article/2518915/the-world-s-most-unusual-outsourcing-destination.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Nosotek之前開發的遊戲包括《The Big Lebowski Bowling》、《Men in Black: Alien Assault》以及《Bobby's Blocks》<ref name="Computerworld: Nosotek" /><ref name="HuffPost: News">{{Cite web|title=Want To Play A Video Game From The Most Isolated Country On Earth?|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/pyongyang-racer-north-korea-video-game_n_2348500|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2012-12-23|work=HuffPost|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142644/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/pyongyang-racer-north-korea-video-game_n_2348500|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《平壤賽車》是受高麗旅行社委托爲其製作的[[廣告遊戲|廣告遊戲]]，高麗旅行社是一家總部設立于[[北京市|北京市]]的[[英國|英國]][[旅行社|旅行社]]，主要負責組織赴朝鮮旅游<ref name="Vice: History" /><ref name="The Verge: News" />。該遊戲的創作靈感始於高麗旅行社的經理尼克·邦納（{{lang|en|Nick Bonner}}）向Nosotek公司的沃爾克·埃洛瑟（{{lang|en|Volker Eloesser}}）提出合作為朝鮮的青年設計一款“有趣的、非血腥和非政治性”的遊戲，並在[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国政府|朝鲜民主主义人民共和国政府]]的支持下，開發商與[[金策工業綜合大學|金策工業綜合大學]]學生合作在[[Adobe_Flash|Adobe Flash]]系統開發了平壤賽車遊戲<ref name="Vice: History" /><ref name="HG101: Review" />。根據遊戲官方網站的説法，《平壤賽車》“并非旨在成爲21世紀令人驚奇的具有高端技術的遊戲，而更多會成爲一種有趣的競賽遊戲（[[街機遊戲|街機]]風格）”<ref name="Vice: History" /><ref name="The Verge: News" />。

《平壤賽車》于2012年12月19日通過其官方網站免費發佈該遊戲，並向全球開放訪問<ref name="HG101: Review" /><ref name="Twitter: Release">{{Cite web|title=Are you fast enough for the Koryo Tours Pyongyang Racer game? Have a bit of retro fun with a free Christmas gift...|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112073534/https://twitter.com/koryotours/status/281306963671920640|access-date=2022-04-23|work=[[Twitter|Twitter]]|language=en}}</ref>。該遊戲因其古怪之處而受到對朝鮮感興趣的人的歡迎，網站訪問亦曾多次遭到中斷<ref name="Slate: News">{{Cite web|title=Drive Deserted Streets in North Korea’s Super-Depressing New Video Game|url=https://slate.com/technology/2012/12/drive-deserted-streets-in-north-korea-s-super-depressing-new-video-game.html|access-date=2022-04-23|date=2012-12-20|last=Eördögh|first=Fruzsina|work=Slate Magazine|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142728/https://slate.com/technology/2012/12/drive-deserted-streets-in-north-korea-s-super-depressing-new-video-game.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 評價 ==
《平壤賽車》一經發行便遭到了多個負面評價：《{{tsl|en|Tech in Asia|亞洲科技}}》的C. Custer評價該遊戲的圖像“非常糟糕”，認爲“充滿了諸多[[小故障|小故障]]和{{tsl|en|Visual artifact|人为视觉效果|人工僞影}}”，還指出遊戲場景重複并且[[帧率|帧率]]低下<ref name="Tech in Asia: Review">{{Cite web|title=Tech in Asia - Connecting Asia's startup ecosystem|url=https://www.techinasia.com/north-korea-computer-game-pyongyang-racer|access-date=2022-04-23|work=www.techinasia.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220112142731/https://www.techinasia.com/north-korea-computer-game-pyongyang-racer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]]》雜志的Nadja Sayej同樣感嘆該遊戲人烟稀少的景象，她聲稱這會給人帶來[[薩斯喀徹溫省|薩斯喀徹溫省]]和[[安大略省|安大略省]]農村的視覺炫目。還引證了遊戲簡單的玩法，將其概述為“長時間直綫行駛”，稱遊戲“非常無趣”<ref name="Vice: History" />。Sayej同意[[美國|美國]]在綫[[大衆媒體|大衆媒體]]公司《{{tsl|en|Jalopnik}}》的Jason Torchinsky的看法，認爲這款遊戲“進程緩慢，非常無趣、空洞、極其受限，并在技術上至少落後了十年時間<ref name="Vice: History" /><ref name="Jalopnik: Review" />”。卡斯特將該遊戲描述爲“糟糕的”，因爲它缺乏挑戰性、車輛速度緩慢并且操控性差<ref name="Tech in Asia: Review" />，他還認爲該遊戲的音效“很難不被人嘲笑”，而托爾欽斯基則稱該遊戲“給玩家帶來的煩惱持續不斷並令人驚訝”。兩人均表示，這款遊戲無意間讓人感覺像是對現實平壤市的諷刺或挖苦性的評價<ref name="Jalopnik: Review" /><ref name="Tech in Asia: Review" />。

